About Us Technology Pipeline Contact Us A biotechnology company developing the next generation of therapeutics for intractable mental health About us Our mission is to map the biological basis of the varieties of psychedelic experience, and to use that map to pharmacologically design therapeutic states of mind to be applied in medically supervised settings to heal the root causes of mental health It is that the therapeutic efficacy of psychedelic compounds is dependent on the quality of the acute experience that they These compounds are effective because they produce a temporary shift to a state of mind that is in some way fundamentally different from the form of normal waking consciousness that we all Those states can be combined with carefully controlled clinical protocols to produce acute experiential therapies with efficacy that far exceeds the current standard of To overcome the shortcomings of current translational models, the development of new psychedelic compounds requires a robust predictive model of acute effects in Our team of neuroscientists, medicinal chemists, computational experts, and drug development veterans is applying our predictive platform to develop the safest and most effective therapies in the current generation of psychedelic states, and to develop entirely novel states that expand the frontiers of psychedelic Technology Our Osmanthus® platform is the leading platform for the prediction of phenomenological psychedelic Osmanthus® is the result of over two decades of natural history study of the varieties of psychedelic experience combined with broad assays of qualitatively distinct psychedelic We are continuing to build out what is already the world’s most robust database of phenomenological and biochemical data on psychedelic compounds: 7,000 experience reports synthesized with assays of dozens of compounds against receptors, transporters, and ion With natural history and computational methods, we’re continuing to discover new biochemical correlations that allow us to specific, discrete states of mind which can be applied in a therapeutic Pipeline Target validation Lead identification Lead optimization studies - Treatment Resistant PTSD - Treatment Resistant Depression We’re applying our platform first to develop the safest and most effective therapies in the first generation of psychedelic states, which have already been clinically validated as breakthrough treatments for mental health 1,2 Our lead program produces an entactogenic state with a superior safety profile to Reduced toxicity and tolerance will allow an increase in number of treatment sessions, leading to superior Our second program produces a state of oceanic boundlessness (commonly called “ego loss”) that can be elicited with a higher degree of reliability than This effect is the primary predictor of treatment outcomes with Additional programs in development produce entirely novel states that expand the frontiers of psychedelic References How it Works - PixieBrix Home Product Features Plans How it Works Security Solutions Sales Customer Service RPA and Digital COEs Developers Marketplace Resources Quick Start Documentation Community YouTube Channel Blog Login Start for Free How it Works PixieBrix is a set of building blocks – we call them “Bricks” – which can be combined to create custom integrations and Each Brick abstracts away the complexity of writing code, while combining Bricks enables a practical level of flexibility to satisfy many use PixieBrix deploys as a Chrome Web Browser Integrations that you develop in PixieBrix live inside your web browser and can interact with any website you visit, including SaaS, proprietary web apps, and PixieBrix can also call into web services and APIs Types of Bricks Whether you re building a basic blueprint with a couple bricks, or need to automate a complex workflow, we ve got you covered Foundations Foundations are things you can “see” such as buttons and Buttons can be used to trigger workflows, while panels embed information from somewhere else on the web Readers Readers do just that — read data or “scrape” a They can extract data from a page s HTML or read data directly from the most popular web frameworks Effects Effects take an input and perform an Effects range from opening a new tab, to inputting text into a search bar, to appending a row to a spreadsheet Transforms Transforms take an input and produce an Examples of this include calling an API, running a JSON transform, and parsing text Renderers Renderers show information on a page as an interactive web component or static Examples include rendering Markdown, or showing data in a table Services Services are reusable resources and configuration, such as a Google Sheet or Slack As their name suggests, they can also be used to authenticate requests to service By creating a PixieBrix account, you can securely share service configurations with your team Join our newsletter! We only transmit and store data required to provide our Data from websites you visit never leaves your browser unless you tell it Our Privacy and Security Policy provides complete details on what data is accessed, transmitted, and Hosting Our Web Application is hosted in the United States, on Salesforce Heroku (Common Runtime) . Heroku is built on Amazon Web We also use Amazon S3 for hosting public media uploads (e.g., Marketplace screenshots). Our Privacy and Security Policy provides a complete list of our service Encryption at Rest Web Application data is encrypted at rest with , Encryption in Transit All internal Web Application traffic, as well as traffic between the Browser Extension and Web Application is encrypted with Transport Layer Security (TLS). You can check the encryption status with Qualys SSL Labs . Backup and Disaster Recovery Web Application data is automatically backed up and can be rolled back up to 4 Vulnerability Scanning Our software dependencies are automatically scanned for vulnerabilities using GitHub s Dependabot service . TIL Therapies Allogeneic Immunotherapy cGMP Manufacturing The Excellos Difference About Us Leadership Team In the News Excelling in Science (Blog) Contact Us TIL Therapies Providing PBMC feeder cells to support TIL therapies TIL (tumor-infiltrating lymphocyte) therapy is a type of cellular immunotherapy that may be used to treat multiple tumor TIL therapy essentially uses altered tumor cells to destroy the tumor The following is an overview of the steps involved: The first step is to surgically remove the tumor from the The tumor is then dissected to remove immune cells that have penetrated the These cells are known as lymphocytes TILs are then cultured and expanded using , resulting in a large population of immune 2 nd and 3 rd generation cell therapies are evolving toward the use of genetically modified However, one of the technical difficulties in genetically modifying TIL for a clinical expansion is the ability to achieve the target expansion, while keeping the technique suitable to a cGMP After a brief course of chemotherapy, TILs are infused back into the patient, where they selectively attack only the cancer Excellos Allogeneic Feeder Cells The generation of the TIL transfer product is challenging with sufficient expansion being notoriously A key component of any rapid expansion protocol is the allogeneic feeder It has been shown that accessory cells in the T cell culture environment can facilitate lymphocyte To support your TIL rapid expansion protocol, Excellos provides irradiated allogeneic peripheral blood mononuclear cells (PBMCs) from healthy donors for T cell Our PBMCs are irradiated using radiation at a dosage that allows retention of their native costimulatory abilities but renders them incompetent for Contact Us to Order PBMC Feeder Cells All “feeder” cells are obtained by apheresis of healthy donors in our donor All donors (collected under consent) undergo testing for infectious diseases with common pathogens and viruses including RPR, Animoca Brands, ranked in the Financial Times list of High Growth Companies , is a leader in digital entertainment, blockchain, and Animoca Brands develops and publishes a broad portfolio of products including the REVV token and SAND token original games including The Sandbox, Crazy Kings, and Crazy Defense Heroes and products utilizing popular intellectual properties including Formula 1®, Marvel, WWE, Power Rangers, MotoGP™, and Animoca Brands’ portfolio of blockchain investments and partnerships includes Sky Mavis (Axie Infinity), Dapper Labs (CryptoKitties and NBA Top Shot), OpenSea, Harmony, Bitski, and Alien Its subsidiaries include The Sandbox, Blowfish Studios, Quidd, Gamee, nWay, Pixowl, and What is Hispanic Heritage Foundation ? Established by the White House in , the Hispanic Heritage Foundation (HHF) is an nonprofit that identifies, inspires, prepares and positions Latino leaders in the classroom, community and workforce to meet America’s HHF’s work is focused on “a Latino to help hundreds more” through a unique cycle of leadership built on a , continuum of sustainable programs, including the Hispanic Heritage Youth Awards, Latinos On Fast Track (LOFT), Hispanic Heritage Awards and Public Awareness About Latino Community Foundation LCF was founded in as an affinity group of United Way of the Bay Area to increase workplace donations to Latino In , Sandra Hernandez, then President and CEO of The San Francisco Foundation (TSFF), established the Foundation as a supporting organization of TSFF, appointed new leadership, and expanded the work of In , LCF became an independent statewide foundation on a mission to unleash the power of Latinos in Uniquely positioned at the intersection of corporate, political and grassroots power, LCF creates and nurtures relationships designed to accelerate impact in unprecedented To date, LCF has created the largest network of Latino philanthropists in the country, invested over $17M in grassroots nonprofits across the State, and launched one of the largest campaigns to mobilize the Latino vote in LCF hosts the Latino Nonprofit Accelerator, a groundbreaking capacity building initiative that gives grassroots nonprofits access to world class branding and fundraising The Rising Tide Network The Rising Tide Network is a diverse group of investors, founders and professionals who have decided to collaborate and support each other’s Each member of the Rising Tide Network has agreed to commit capital, connections, and advice to help each other’s projects Initially, this is an opportunity to get early access to companies founded by experienced entrepreneurs within our community, but the broader purpose is to leverage this network to provide investment and mentorship for future generations of underserved Who are the artists we are trying to support? Litepaper - Dexalot Dexalot Exchange Governance Resources Litepaper Articles Tutorials FAQ Litepaper Secure, Fast, Low Cost Contents Executive Summary Introduction Exchange Overview Technology Privacy Matching Algorithm Governance Strategic Road Map Conclusion Dexalot Exchange Executive Summary Dexalot’s mission is to bring the traditional exchange experience - namely the Central Limit Order Book capability - in a decentralized manner through the use of a fast and scalable blockchain - Dexalot is built on Avalanche platform’s technology for its implementation as it offers the following advantages: % compatibility with the mature Ethereum Virtual Machine Transactional speeds with second Transactional throughput that can withstand thousands of transactions per Low cost of deployment and Introduction Dexalot is an exchange aiming at bringing the traditional centralized exchange user experience without compromising on decentralization and As such Dexalot implements an Central Limit Order Book for its trade pairs on the Avalanche Dexalot allows for users to trade ERC20 tokens supported on the against the blockchain native currency Users can also trade supported ERC20 tokens against other supported ERC20 Dexalot has three differentiating characteristics that set it apart from other centralized and decentralized exchanges: Ability to place limit orders full Traders can set the size and limit price for their If an order matches an existing order in the order book in terms of price, it removes liquidity (taker order) and executes If there are no immediate matches in the order book, the order will be added to the order book as a new maker Taker orders do not have to be (AON) as Dexalot supports partially filled orders where the unfilled portion of an order automatically enters the order book as a maker Dexalot supports market orders as well but this functionality will be turned on for trade pairs individually that reach appropriate liquidity Inclusion of users through governance Dexalot will implement a governance model as well as create incentives for it s loyal users in the near A strong community ownership and participation in governance is an important goal for the Built on Avalanche Dexalot chose the Avalanche platform for its obvious advantages in speed, throughput and Previous attempts to bring Central Limit Order Book Functionality on blockchains with inferior consensus protocols typically led to limited adoption, high slippage and large amounts of market risk for the Dexalot solves these problems by operating on the and it will also look to further improve usability and user experience by potentially moving the technology to a subnet after key platform updates and adequate Exchange Overview Dexalot is accessible through the website at https: www.dexalot.com compatible with recent versions of Chrome, Edge, Brave, Opera and Firefox desktop Dexalot will initially support Metamask and traders will need to install the extension (or the mobile application) to be able to MetaMask is the initial wallet integration of choice due to its wide adoption and proven track Dexalot will integrate more wallets in the future to provide additional flexibility to All transactions that lead to a state change on the blockchain (depositing funds into Dexalot smart contract, withdrawing funds from Dexalot smart contract, placing limit order into the orderbook, taking liquidity by trading against an order in the book via either limit or market order and cancelling existing orders) require a confirmation via the MetaMask wallet and network transaction The network transaction fee is inherent to the Avalanche platform and it is always paid from the wallet of the trader initiating the Activity on the Dexalot platform will also incur an additional platform fee which is collected by the smart contract and will be used for enhancing the Technology All smart contracts are coded in Solidity and they are available from the project github repository with an license at https: github.com dexalot contracts (link will be activated shortly before launch). Dexalot’s collection of smart contracts makes extensive use of OpenZeppelin upgradeable contracts available from https: github.com OpenZeppelin openzeppelin-contracts-upgradeable . All traders and smart contract enthusiasts are welcome to scrutinize the code for security and become part of the Dexalot’s smart contracts are fully audited by Ava Labs and Hacken The Dexalot platform is made up of components that provide various services: User Wallet: Users will utilize their wallets (Metamask to start) to connect and interact with Frontend: This is the user interface for Dexalot where users can view the order book, place orders, cancel existing orders and can track their Backend This is the server side infrastructure that is responsible for responding to the interactions from the frontend, recording the transaction activity into the database, and serving data back to the Smart Contracts This is the c

Trying to Conceive - Posterity Health Skip to main content Hit enter to search or ESC to close Close Search Schedule an Appointment Login Menu About Us Services Male Fertility Topics Trying to Conceive Equity in Fertility TTC Timelines Partners Contact Us Schedule an Appointment Login Home » Trying to Conceive Trying to Conceive It’s the question you’ve answered too many times as the months drag “When are you two going to have a baby?” “We’re trying” is your automatic The word trying sums up the experience for many couples who are trying to conceive (TTC). It is trying to go month after month without a positive pregnancy It is trying to mourn after a It is trying to see friends get pregnant … without even It is exciting, stressful, painful, expensive, sad, depressing and scary to be trying to have a baby with no end in Whether you are starting to try, or have been trying for months or years, knowing more about the male reproductive system will help reframe your understanding of fertility and your approach to TTC – conceiving and achieving a healthy pregnancy by taking a comprehensive look at the ‘sperm + egg = pregnancy’ Fast Facts You’re far from alone Infertility is defined as not being able to get pregnant after trying with unprotected sex for one year, or 6 months of trying if over years In the US, 1 in 8 couples (15%) are unable to get pregnant after a year of having unprotected sex . And age matters, 1 in 6 couples over the age of have difficulty getting It takes two Infertility is as common in men as it is in Pause and take that Approximately % of infertility is due solely to sperm or male factors, % can be attributed solely to egg or female factors, % to a combination of both partners, and % of cases have an unknown Meaning male fertility issues affect at least half of couples struggling to conceive . Many couples struggle unnecessarily to conceive and for extended periods of time simply because the male’s reproductive health is overlooked (that sperm part of the equation). Given male and female factors contribute equally to difficulty conceiving, assessing the reproductive health of the male concurrently with the female is a logical step when evaluating options and optimizing changes to achieve a healthy It’s so much more than just ejaculating Remember in middle school sex ed when they told us … “if you have sex, you will get pregnant” …turns out there’s so much more to it, and it’s never too late to get a better understanding of male reproductive anatomy and all the other stuff that goes into, well, the stuff that eventually comes Who you are, and what you do influences your sperm quantity and quality – from genetics to lifestyle, hormones to Importantly, checking on your swimmers with a semen analysis (fertility test for men) and if abnormal – an evaluation with a male fertility specialist can identify factors that are oftentimes reversible or treatable, not to mention the possibility of diagnosing an underlying medical condition presenting as Whether you are looking to become a dad for the first time, or you are adding to your brood, taking a holistic approach to managing your health, starting with your fertility, best prepares you for the parenting journey Male Fertility Myths Masculinity = fertility Stereotypical heterosexual alpha males are no more or less likely to be fertile than other In fact, anabolic steroids and synthetic testosterone are known to interfere with sperm So, ironically, these lifestyle choices can actually negatively impact If you have a history of anabolic steroid or testosterone use and are trying to become a father, a male fertility test – semen analysis – can determine if you have a normal sperm If not, a male fertility specialist can create a plan with you to manage your testosterone while optimizing sperm Beyond just physical appearances, our societal view of masculinity includes the expectation that a masculine male is one who has the ability to achieve professional success, produce offspring and provide for his While these stereotypes are deeply rooted in our culture, we are starting to see change and understanding that high achieving, successful males are no more or less likely to be fertile than other Male factor infertility or a low sperm count is not a measure of masculinity, it is a medical condition that is most often treatable! It is what it is, there’s nothing I can do about it Like the ladies, your health impacts your Lifestyle choices, including smoking, drinking alcohol, recreational drug use and your diet and nutrition play an important role in semen Obesity is associated with a decrease in sperm quality and an increased risk of Fortunately, overcoming these negative effects on fertility are often achieved by making healthier lifestyle For males with underlying health issues and chronic conditions, it’s especially important to seek care from a qualified male fertility specialist to understand the effects any medication or behaviors have on fertility, a

Coherence 0 Skip to Content Coherence Open Menu Close Menu Open Menu Close Menu Coherence Empower your software team to solve the problems that matter, not the problems that get in the Our Story As a technology leader building teams at startups over the last years, I’ve had to solve the same problems over and again, across both infrastructure and In talking to my peers, the feeling of is In spite of the applicability of best practices (CI CD, Infra as code, security, MVPs, iterative development, automation, monitoring observability), each team goes through the same cycle across the Generally the infrastructure always has gaps between what’s done and the “whitepaper” - because getting to “good enough” is what the business cares about and there’s work to be done that customers Coherence aims to build vertically integrated development experiences that involve less “glue” and “yak ” For us, vertical integration means understanding that the SDLC starts before code is written and ends after code is Our tools should make it easy to think about these needs holistically, to move between stages of them seamlessly, and to do better than “good enough” when configuring and managing When we look years into the future, our hope is that software development will not involve so much configuration and coordination and that the day to day will be more seamless and Ultimately development teams will be more inclusive and help companies get closer to what their users and customers need! We have founded Coherence because we’re excited to help make that future a We believe that development teams in the century should have a “10x” better toolkit that lets them focus on understanding and delivering value for their We’re excited to show you what that toolkit looks If you’re excited to help make these tools a reality and build a world class company, great!
